      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey i'm working on this blog post called \"The Global Standard for Professionalism\" and i want to make it a guide for people traveling for work. basically what are the essential rules for being seen as a sophisticated, high-level professional regardless of where you are in the world? like what are the universal norms for things like dress and how you carry yourself in meetings?",
